### **3. 29_LogBurstCanvas**  
**Description:**  
Detects repetition storms, burst clusters, and error patterns across log files.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LogBurstCanvas - Burst-Aware Log Pattern Analyzer

LogBurstCanvas highlights when errors spike or patterns repeat abnormally within your log streams.

## Features
- Burst and frequency analysis  
- Timestamp pattern mapping  
- CLI with keyword filters  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/29_LogBurstCanvas.git
cd 29_LogBurstCanvas
python analyze.py logs/system.log
